<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>{{serviceName}} Subscription Expired</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Your {{serviceName}} Subscription has Expired</h1>
    <p>
      We regret to inform you that your subscription has expired. However, you
      are now within a 15-day grace period. During this time, you can still
      access your data and renew your subscription by paying the outstanding
      invoice.
    </p>
    <p>
      Please click the link below to view and pay your invoice:
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{invoiceUrl}}">Pay Invoice</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      If you do not renew your subscription before the end of the grace period,
      all data associated with your subscription will be terminated.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or need assistance, please do not hesitate to
      contact us.
    </p>
    <p>Best Regards,</p>
    <p>The {{serviceName}} Team</p>
  </body>
</html>